column2: SELECT TOP # nsaid, ra, dec, z, (#*z/#) as Dist, (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.#) as AbsMag, (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.# # +#*LOG1# (#*#*z/#) ) as AppMag, (.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.#) as Color, (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.# # +#*log (#*#*z/#, #) +#*LOG1# (#*PI () *POWER ((#*elpetro_th5#_g-elpetro_th5#_r) , #) )#*LOG1# (#+z) ) as SBe, elpetro_absmag_g as g, elpetro_absmag_r as r, elpetro_th5#_g as g_radius, elpetro_th5#_r as r_radius, elpetro_mets as Metallicity, elpetro_mass as Mass FROM nsatlas WHERE (#*#*z/#) > # AND dec> # AND elpetro_mass> # AND (#*z/#) < # AND (.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.#) < # AND (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.#) < # AND (elpetro_absmag_g+.#* (elpetro_absmag_g-elpetro_absmag_r) +.# # +#*log (#*#*z/#, #) +#*LOG1# (#*PI () *POWER ((#*elpetro_th5#_g-elpetro_th5#_r) , #) )#*LOG1# (#+z) )< #
